Package: colouRmaps
Title: Colourful Maps for Cooler Graphics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Paul", "Goodall", , "paul.thomas.goodall@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6193-6529"))
Description: Creates a set of useful colourmaps to use when creating graphs. Some of the colour tables herein were taken from STARLINK's GAIA distribution, where they have the GNU copyleft. Further information on STARLINK and GAIA can be found via http://star-www.rl.ac.uk/ and http://star-www.dur.ac.uk/~pdraper/
